BOARD OF COUNTY COMMISSIONERS OF THE COUNTY OF PROWERS v. ATCHI-SON, TOPEKA & SANTA FÉ, RAILWAY COMPANY. No. 427. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 1, 1931. William R. Kelly, of Greeley, Colo., and John R. Wolff, of Boulder, Colo., for appellant. Erl H. Ellis, of Denver, Colo., for ap-pellee.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and Me-DERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 1,1931, per stipulation.
